Gets info about the running Valorant process including start arguments  

Variables:
 - `{lockfile password}` and `{lockfile port}`: Read [Common Components - Lockfile Data](https://github.com/techchrism/valorant-api-docs/tree/trunk/docs/common-components.md#lockfile-data)


### Response Format:
```ts
{
    [x: string]: {
        exitCode: number;
        exitReason: null;
        isInternal: boolean;
        launchConfiguration: {
            arguments: string[];
            executable: string;
            locale: string | null;
            voiceLocale: null;
            workingDirectory: string;
        };
        patchlineFullName: "VALORANT" | "riot_client";
        patchlineId: "" | "live" | "pbe";
        phase: string;
        productId: "valorant" | "riot_client";
        version: string;
    };
}
```

